{
    "type": "script",
    "id": "f2c9b9b7-a4e9-4202-ae4c-1173b654816c",
    "name": "Magic Class Session 1 08 Spark Stone",
    "sceneId": "981d126b-abc7-430a-abb4-e912340c59e6",
    "trigger": {
        "type": "triggers.manual",
        "name": "Manual"
    },
    "entryPoints": [
        {
            "type": "scripts.entryPoint",
            "id": "5d2efbb9-fe13-4785-a5e3-5c50390a9d03",
            "name": "Main",
            "nodes": [
                {
                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                    "id": "6347cdb8-e2b0-4be9-aecf-985f7f41b6a2",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "amount": "2",
                    "change": "1",
                    "notify": true
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "1ea08c17-a540-47a9-bced-b1625d9ad480",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "For this lesson, we will be the same techniques that you learned in yesterday's lesson to construct a very different runestone. ",
                    "emotion": "1",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "4c4532e2-88f8-42db-8407-e763b2a2edd2",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "I know that many of you are going to face dangerous situations in your life that will involve physical combat. Therefore, your next lessons will be centered around magical offense and defense.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "89cff75b-0750-4de2-ba37-c7edca3e5be5",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Today, you will learn the runes that will enhance your weapon to do more damage. It is called the <i>Spark</i> spell.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "c34db29f-b1b3-4017-bff5-7fe257277fa6",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "The <i>Spark</i> spell will add magical energy to the weapon you are currently wielding. This effect will last for the duration of one combat. You will need to reactivate the spell whenever you engage in battle.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "abcc9fdd-2627-495d-a493-65e31da52dca",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "The activation mantra for this spell is \"Fulmen Cio\" or \"invoke the lightning.\"",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "id": "ce06bd57-ea9a-4b2b-957b-b78e33f35dd6",
                    "type": "nodes.improveSkill",
                    "skill": "Magic",
                    "amount": "2",
                    "notify": true
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "e823022a-38bf-42db-b512-1119352ac914",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Are there any questions before we begin?",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.showMenu",
                    "id": "1b92b374-d5d7-4db7-a83e-bb4fcf360a23",
                    "options": [
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "1aada3ba-646f-48aa-9c6c-be9c88902ff1",
                            "text": "Ask About the Spark Spell and the Undead",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "e9ef0a1f-dcea-44b6-a39b-b2bf24c29e13",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "text": "Does the Spark spell make a weapon magical enough to do damage to Undead and ghostly thingies?",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "7b1d828c-fca0-4728-8625-16209a7c8723",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Yes, this will give an ordinary weapon the ability to damage non-corporeal creatures. However, it won't do a great deal of damage against them, so I suggest you avoid such monstrosities all together.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                    "id": "fac48172-414c-446e-a287-b933d099adcf",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "amount": "2",
                                    "change": "1",
                                    "notify": true
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "4",
                            "ExitMenu": false
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "83222adf-f5dd-4e4c-bf91-6b86fcc90bfa",
                            "text": "Ask About Runestones",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "d5f20f8a-7aff-42da-8d55-1ad44599dc70",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "text": "Do runestones run out of magic and stop working if you use them too much?",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "79d6cd7b-32e2-4c12-9f7b-ce8fcfb7b5f0",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "A well-made runestone can last as long as it isn't damaged. After all, you will be using your own Mojo to activate the spell. The runestone is merely a focus for the spell.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                    "id": "24d8bdb4-2e39-4aa2-8c8f-3539d82ad362",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "amount": "2",
                                    "change": "1",
                                    "notify": true
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "3",
                            "ExitMenu": false
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "abaa04de-6004-404e-b295-f92b413d2115",
                            "text": "Ask About Forgetting the Mantra",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "15aef323-3c4f-462e-929b-a3d9b2f73590",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "text": "What happens if we forget the magic words... the mantra... to invoke a runestone? Will other words work, too?",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "01da5141-fa85-4e5a-b872-16e00ce2fdad",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Words are very powerful symbols. A spell is shaped and defined by the words we use to cast it. You must know the specific mantra for each runestone in order to cast its spell. ",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "494bcb50-4d3e-438b-96e1-a25a9da56853",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Magic invocation is not frippery mumbo-jumbo. It is precise and concise.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                    "id": "293245dd-ca1b-4690-8d26-cc1925f89851",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "amount": "1",
                                    "change": "1",
                                    "notify": true
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "5",
                            "ExitMenu": false
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "9b8c972b-5618-4f5c-a1f4-c03470b088d5",
                            "text": "Make a Joke About Wizards",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "df07339e-8f44-4a33-ada0-7f6b81733c42",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "text": "What did the tipsy Wizard say when she looked at criminal activities on her crystal ball?",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "dcbd4b5a-c6d1-4c86-98ec-e35e07c3a097",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "I have no idea what you are talking about.",
                                    "emotion": "4",
                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "100004a5-9f11-4c5b-9e6b-fa2769bae7e1",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "text": "The Wizard said, \"My, how crime scries when you are having rum!\"",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "29a62afb-6443-4556-94c8-257d2e287557",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Oh, I see! This is a sort of a joke. How droll...",
                                    "emotion": "4",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "id": "113bc31c-b569-43fd-97b4-5942473b2d21",
